    <stitle>HENDRICKSON SUSPENSION SYSTEMS - BUSHING REPLACEMENT - BEAM OVERHAUL (IN SHOP)</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="replace" graphiccount="0">
        <title>BEAM OVERHAUL (IN SHOP)</title>
        <para>When overhauling a (walking) beam assembly, use shop tools and press. Use the SPECIAL TOOL, BEAM BUSHING
            TOOL SET. Follow tool instructions. Refer to SPECIAL TOOLS,
            <hotlnk document="s03006s_30.xml" xrefid="f0300644">Figure 44</hotlnk>,
            <hotlnk document="s03006s_30.xml" xrefid="f0300645">Figure 45</hotlnk>, and
            <hotlnk document="s03006s_30.xml" xrefid="f0300646">Figure 46</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <para>Inspect beam cross tube ends for wear and for being bent. If any of these conditions is found, replace the
            tube.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
